[src:abortion-in-colorado/abortion-in-alaska] The event was organized by Planned Parenthood Votes and Alaska ACLU.
[src:abortion-in-colorado/abortion-in-alaska] There was another rally at the Alaska Capitol in Juneau in May 2019, in opposition to the bill proposed by Republican Rep.
